data.meta_description:
10 likes, 0 comments - gtlibrary on September 22, 2023: "Today’s Author Feature Friday: The incomparable C.J. Cherryh. 

Cherryh has won the Hugo Award for Best Novel twice, plus another win for Best Short Story and the Locus Award for best Science Fiction Novel. 

We have her work both in the Circulating Science Fiction Collection on Crosland 1 and online. You can check out short stories, long-form novels, and critical reception and critique of her work.".
